{"tid":1843960,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發第一槍 瑪麗醫院內科B6病房罷工","createTime":"2020-01-26T12:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T12:49:10.000Z","uid":5195,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"165672c938468eac5e79c25c7ac84b90dd8fd0ce","tid":1843960,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/medicalinspire/photos/a.215810405740451/504868690167953?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmedicalinspire%2Fphotos%2Fa.215810405740451%2F504868690167953%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=b3d0c1b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/medicalinspire/photos/a.215810405740451/504868690167953?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMedical Inspire收到獨家醫護報料，瑪麗醫院內科呼吸系統專科B6病房，現在已經成為「隔離病房」，但前線醫護指，所有該病房的註冊護士今午一起申請病假，只剩下護士長返工，成為率先實施罷工的醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n#MedicalInspire #袁國勇教授 #武漢肺炎 #醫護罷工 #獨家消息 #瑪麗醫院 #內科病房 #醫思維<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------<br />\n訂閱 YouTube Medical Inspire 醫．思維 專頁：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2TD7WL3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2TD7WL3&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=9169f3b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2TD7WL3</a><br />\n追隨 Instagram Medical Inspire 醫．思維 專頁：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/medicalinspire/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmedicalinspire%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=40472590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/medicalinspire/</a><br />\n訂閱 Telegram Medical Inspire 醫．思維 頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/medicalinspire\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmedicalinspire&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGen4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=11c61207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/medicalinspire</a><br />\n追隨 Twitt